note bottom of BossEnv
  **Dynamic Observation Vector**
  [0-2]  Hero velocity (normalized)
  [3]    Hero combo step
  [4]    Hero attacking (0/1)
  [5]    Hero HP %
  [6]    Distance (normalized)
  [7]    Angle (normalized)
  [8]    Boss HP %
  [9-16] Player profile (8 dims)
  ---- IRL enabled (+5) ----
  [17-21] P(attack|s), P(block|s), P(dodge|s),
          P(approach|s), P(retreat|s)
  ---- Emotion enabled (+3) ----
  [+0] Frustration score [0-1]
  [+1] Flow score [0-1]
  [+2] Boredom score [0-1]
  ---- Max: 25 dims (17+5+3) ----
  ---- With Hierarchical: 29 dims ----
end note

note bottom of UPlayerMemoryComponent
  **Decay Algorithm**
  For each profile dimension i:
  if EncountersSinceActive[i] > threshold:
    profile[i] = lerp(profile[i], 0.5, rate)
  Prevents all-knowing boss.
  Rewards strategy rotation.
end note

note bottom of ConstrainedBossEnv
  **Fun Constraint + Emotion Modulation**
  if win_rate > target + 5%:
    epsilon = min(0.3, excess * 2)
  ---- Extension 10 ----
  Frustrated (>0.6): epsilon += 0.15
  Bored (>0.6): epsilon -> near 0
  Flow (>0.6): maintain stability
end note

note right of HierarchicalAgent
  **Two-Level Policy**
  Strategist: every 30 steps
    -> selects archetype (0-3)
  Tactician: every step
    -> selects action (0-4)
    conditioned on strategy
end note

note bottom of UEmotionEstimationComponent
  **Behavioral Emotion Inference**
  No hardware — purely from game signals
  ---- Frustration (4 factors) ----
  Loss streak (0.4) + duration decrease (0.2)
  + action spam (0.2) + low entropy (0.2)
  ---- Flow (4 factors) ----
  Mixed outcomes (0.35) + close HP (0.25)
  + high entropy (0.2) + stable duration (0.2)
  ---- Boredom (4 factors) ----
  Low action rate (0.3) + idle time (0.25)
  + retreat-heavy (0.25) + easy wins (0.2)
  Ticks at 4 Hz. Fires delegate on state change.
end note

note bottom of MAMLTrainer
  **Meta-Learning Pipeline**
  1. Collect replays from 8+ players (3+ episodes each)
  2. meta_train: 5000 outer iterations
     Sample tasks -> inner adapt -> query eval -> meta-grad
  3. adapt_to_player: 2-3 gradient steps (seconds)
  ---- Key Result ----
  Win rate at 3 MAML steps should match
  transfer learning at 50k fine-tune steps.
end note

note bottom of BossPlanner
  **Deliberative Planning**
  For each boss action (0-4):
    For top-K player actions (via IRL):
      Predict next_obs via WorldModel
      Evaluate via value function or recurse
  Returns highest expected value action.
  Blended with policy: weight * plan + (1-w) * policy
end note

note right of MaxEntIRL
  **Maximum Entropy IRL**
  R(s) = theta^T * phi(s)
  Recovers *why* player acts,
  not just *what* they do.
  ---- Prediction ----
  Top-1 accuracy target: 35-50%
  (vs 20% random baseline)
end note

